//! ActivityPub Federation plugin and event publishing service.
//!
//! Initialises [`activitypub_federation::config::FederationConfig`] at startup,
//! provides server-level AP endpoints (WebFinger, actor, inbox, outbox), and
//! exposes event publishing helpers so that REST and gRPC controllers can
//! broadcast Create / Update / Delete activities to federated peers.
//!
//! ## Configuration
//!
//! | Env variable           | Description                                              |
//! |------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|
//! | `FEDERATION_DOMAIN`    | Public hostname of this instance (default: localhost:8080)|
//! | `FEDERATION_PEERS`     | Comma-separated list of peer instance base URLs           |

